selection

1.start
2.read the size of the array in n
3.create an array of size n (a[n])
4.i=0
5.if(i<n) go to 6 else go to 8
6.read the element into a[i]
7.i++ go to 5
8. i=0
9.  if(i<n) go to 10 else  16
10.j=i+1
11.  if(j<n) go to 12 else go to 15
12  if(a[i]>a[j]) go to 13 else go to 14
13.   temp=a[i],a[i]=a[j],a[j]=temp 
14.   j++ go to 11
15.   i++  go to 9
16.stop